# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  secrets.env.example – credential variable template
#
#  COPY TO: secrets.env (gitignored, do NOT commit)
#    cp secrets.env.example secrets.env
#
#  SCRIPTS THAT USE secrets.env:
#  - scripts/diagnose-airs.sh         (section 4 – cert/SCM connection via SCM API)
#  - future SCM integration scripts
#
#  CREDENTIAL LOOKUP ORDER inside scripts:
#    1. Exported environment variables
#    2. ./secrets.env in PWD (preferred – easy locally)
#    3. .claude/secrets/scm-api.json (gitignored, for Claude Code)
#    4. ~/.claude-scm/scm-api.json   (per-user fallback)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# SCM Service Account credentials
#
# How to generate:
#  1. Sign in to Strata Cloud Manager: https://stratacloudmanager.paloaltonetworks.com
#  2. Settings → Identity & Access → Service Accounts → Add Service Account
#  3. Pick a role: minimum "Tenant Service Group Read-Only"
#     (for diagnostics); for advanced operations use "Tenant Administrator"
#  4. After creation, save the Client ID and Client Secret (Secret is shown ONLY ONCE)
#
# You can find the TSG ID in: SCM → Settings → Tenant → copy the ID (15-digit number)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
SCM_CLIENT_ID="your-service-account@TSGID.iam.panserviceaccount.com"
SCM_CLIENT_SECRET="your-secret-uuid-here"
SCM_TSG_ID="123456789012345"

# ─────────────────────────────────────────
# (Optional) AIRS API key for API Intercept (api-chatbot)
#
# How to generate:
#  1. SCM → AI Security → API Applications → pick the application
#  2. Generate API Key (one key per deployment profile)
#
# This same key also goes into terraform.tfvars (airs_api_key) for the
# deploy-app.sh deployment – this entry is here in case it's needed by
# other scripts.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────
AIRS_API_KEY=""
AIRS_API_ENDPOINT="https://service.api.aisecurity.paloaltonetworks.com"
AIRS_SECURITY_PROFILE_NAME="airs-api-chatbot-profile"
